
Summary
-------
Provides the possibility to add more domains to a site.
This is done by adding a new model: SiteDomain. Domains can
be configured through the site admin UI.

Installation
------------

Generate the migration:

  script/generate plugin_migration multiple_site_domains

Migrate the database:

  rake db:migrate


